<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie=edge")
        title Document
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css")
    body
        .main-container
            h1 Test your reaction time!
            p When you start the test, different shapes will appear. Only click on the circles to score points. Depending on your speed you get more or less points. Click the wrong shape and points will be taken from you. After ten circles have appeared the game ends.
            h3 Circlecount: 
                span#circle-count
            canvas#shape-canvas
            button#start-btn Start
            h2#time-to-start
            .hidden#points-container
                h3 Points:
                p#points
            h2 Results:
            for result in results
                div
                    p Name: #{result.name}
                    p Points: #{result.points}
                    p Date: #{result.date}
                br
        script(src="script.js" type="application/javascript")